OL,8,FWales Police, said: "All nine involved
OL,9,Fwere key figures in this drug supply
OL,10,Fchain and I am thrilled that we have
OL,11,Fbeen able to sentence them for their
OL,12,Fcrimes and remove them from our
OL,13,Fcommunities.J"The sentences passed
OL,14,Fdown send a strong message that drugs
OL,15,Fand organised crime groups (OCG) have
OL,16,Fno place in our communities. Not only
OL,17,Fhave we been able to disrupt this OCG
OL,18,Fand their operation, but we have also
OL,19,Fbeen able to take a large quantity of
OL,20,Fdrugs off the streets."JHe added:
OL,21,F"South Wales Police is committed to
